{"tid":1976503,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"[有感而發] 作為一個差唔多四十歲既阿叔，總覺得英超有陣柒味......","createTime":"2020-04-17T09:38:09.000Z","updateTime":"2020-04-18T09:15:06.000Z","uid":28938,"like":14,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":15,"replies":[{"pid":"0e6364b73349deeca0b1f9be087d1a252c791d2e","tid":1976503,"uid":28938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:38:09.000Z","msg":"我地成長既背景係意甲既黃金年代，果時意甲球員真係有種星味，巴迪斯圖達、巴治奧、馬甸尼......球場內外既表現都好有吸引，戰國七雄鬥戰術鬥星味又好好睇。自己辛苦儲錢去到意大利現場睇波，食Pizza、Gelato、學意大利文 、同D路人係街巷踢下波，感覺意大利真係一個好有足球文化既國家。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/PTuxBZG.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FPTuxBZG.jpg&h=1de5b071&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n睇返依家d小朋友鍾意英超<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，個個球員都係性格巨星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，求其一兩場有表現就叫球星<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，扭屎忽花要求加人工，唔肯拼搏，天生有領袖氣質、魅力既球員好少，真係覺得完全<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">唔撚明</span></span>d小朋友鍾意佢地d咩。<br />\n<br />\n睇下佢地鍾意咩英超球員......普巴、哈利簡尼、連加特，就覺得真係好低層次，完全對足球藝術無理解。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n預感會俾班小朋友負評同狂插<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，純粹有感而發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e5b754cb5b89676ceb50bb780be6d491cb6316b7","tid":1976503,"uid":23815,"like":3,"dislike":2,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:40:24.000Z","msg":"某D球隊啫 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n一係就MMA 一係就皇者 <br />\n<br />\n我利就無呢方面問題 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/give.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"864245aa05b63f00a238aaa1a6634a30d13521b7","tid":1976503,"uid":42246,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-04-17T09:42:29.000Z","msg":"琴日搞完日韓<br />